    <stitle>DT-466E and 530E Diesel Engine Service (1995 through 1999) - SECTION 2: TURBOCHARGERS - REASSEMBLY</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>REASSEMBLY</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="assemble" graphiccount="5">
            <title>ALIGN MARKS OF THE COMPRESSOR HOUSING TO BACKPLATE</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Align marks of the compressor housing to backplate. Attach compressor housing to the
                    backplate.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install wastegate actuator bracket with actuator arm and diaphragm attached to center
                    housing. Secure with three (3) bolts, if equipped. Tighten to standard torque (
                    <emph type="bold">Figure
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600220">2.20</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Connect wastegate actuator arm to wastegate and install retaining clip, if equipped.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Align marks of the wastegate and turbine housing. Attach wastegate housing to turbine
                    housing and secure with six (6) bolts. Tighten bolts (
                    <emph type="bold">Figure
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600221">2.21</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
                <figure id="ef1600219" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg5433" filename="../figeg5/EG5433.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 2.19 Checking Wastegate Valves</caption>
                </figure>
                <figure id="ef1600220" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg5423" filename="../figeg5/EG5423.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 2.20 Install Wastegate Actuator Bracket</caption>
                </figure>
                <figure id="ef1600221" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg5431" filename="../figeg5/EG5431.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 2.21 Install Wastegate Cover</caption>
                </figure>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Align marks of the turbine and center housing. Attach turbine housing to center housing.
                    Secure with four (4) bolts and tighten to special torque value (
                    <emph type="bold">Figure
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600222">2.22</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Using six (6) bolts and two (2) clamps secure compressor housing to backplate. Tighten
                    to the special torque value (
                    <emph type="bold">Figure
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600223">2.23</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>
                            <emph type="underscr">WASTEGATE TURBOCHARGERS ONLY:</emph>
                            USE A NEW ACTUATOR HOSE WHEN REASSEMBLING TURBOCHARGER.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">
                    <emph type="bold">Wastegate Turbocharger Only:</emph>Attach hose from the compressor side of the
                    turbocharger to the wastegate actuator. Secure hose with two (2) hose clamps
                    <emph type="bold">(Figure
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600223">2.23</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
                <figure id="ef1600222" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg5430" filename="../figeg5/EG5430.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 2.22 Installing Turbine Housing</caption>
                </figure>
                <figure id="ef1600223" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg5426" filename="../figeg5/EG5426.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 2.23 Installing Compressor Housing</caption>
                </figure>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
